Package org.jboss.resteasy.plugins.providers.atom.app

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppAccept
    Per RFC5023:

    The content of an "app:accept" element value is a media range as defined in [RFC2616].
    AppCategories
    The app:categories element can contain a "fixed" attribute, with a value of either "yes" or "no", indicating whether the list of categories is a fixed or an open set.
    AppCollection
    Per RFC5023:

    The "app:collection" element describes a Collection.
    AppCommonAttributes
    Attributes common across all atom app types
    AppService
    Per RFC 5023:

    The root of a Service Document is the "app:service" element.
    AppWorkspace
    Per RFC5023:

    A Service Document groups Collections into Workspaces.
    BooleanAdapter
